latestPosts.caption:
One of my favorite surgeries to perform: EVO ICL.

This groundbreaking refractive procedure is quickly becoming one of the most popular surgeries around the world for improving vision. The EVO ICL enhances natural vision with a biocompatible lens that can stay in place for life (or be removed if needed). Fast recovery, no dry eye, and treats even strong prescriptions and astigmatism.

As a surgeon, it’s incredibly rewarding to witness with so many of my patients called life-changing.

Whether you want bold volume, natural definition, waterproof wear, or precise lengthening, Clinique has a formula for every lash type:
